data.description:
Just in time! Newly adjusted price!
Recently renovated and ready for new owner! Charming & well-maintained home featuring a spacious floor plan with large rooms, updated flooring, & fresh paint throughout, tons of natural light, new roof & gutters (2.5y), updated bathrooms, new lighting fixtures & fans, cozy kitchen with large central island & stainless steel appliances, and a massive primary suite with dual closets & en suite bathroom. Large, low maintenance lot with ample curb appeal and a private fenced-in backyard featuring an above-ground pool, outdoor entertainment cabana area, & plenty of yard space with bonus storage shed all in a quiet neighborhood with quick access to countless surrounding amenities. Motivated Seller!
